&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Minimal Payloads&lt;/strong&gt; - Include only necessary data&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Clear Event Names&lt;/strong&gt; - Use descriptive event naming conventions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Versioning Strategy&lt;/strong&gt; - Plan for webhook payload evolution&lt;/li&gt;
