&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Batch Processing&lt;/strong&gt; - Group related events when possible&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Retry Logic&lt;/strong&gt; - Implement intelligent retry mechanisms&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Monitoring&lt;/strong&gt; - Continuous webhook performance monitoring&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Error Handling&lt;/strong&gt; - Graceful error handling and logging&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Troubleshooting&lt;span class=&#34;hx:absolute hx:-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;troubleshooting&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
